Description: The flight into Egypt; the Virgin with the Child is led by St Joseph, facing right; on a column to the left is an graven image which breaks apart Metalcut with hand-colouring
Curator's comments: Part of "The fall of man, the life and passion of Christ," a series of forty cuts. See the comment for the first print from the series, registered as 1912-8-8-34 (Schreiber 2389.a).
Bibliographic references: Schreiber 1926-1930 / Handbuch der Holz- und Metalschnitte des XV Jahrhunderts (2212.m)
Leidinger 1908 / Vierzig Metallschnitte des XV. Jahrhunderts aus Münchener Privatbesitz (9)
Acquisition notes: The entire series 1912,0808.1 to 40 was presented by a single anonymous donor.
